featuredSessions.description: Join us for the first Cloud Next'18 Extended Targu Mures event, where we'll bring together cloud enthusiasts and the developer community to be a part of the cloud experience. Next Extended allows local developers to access exciting Next ‘18 content and engage with the community through local speakers, activities, and hands-on labs.

team.description:
[IT Mures Group](https://www.facebook.com/groups/itmures/) - is open and volunteer geek community who create exciting projects and share experience about technologies with a passion. Our mission is to connect Mures based IT Professionals, building community, discussing new tech, events, meetups, opportunities!

Our goal is to organize space to connect the best industry experts with IT Mures audience to boost development of IT.

Developers see much more: APIs, scalability issues, mobile, web, automotive, complex technology stacks. And that is what IT Mures is about.
